      "rationale": "Code verification performed using the Taylor-Couette rotating flow benchmark at Re = 1200, matching the impeller-gap Reynolds number range of the CPB operating envelope. Observed order of accuracy p = 1.94 (theoretical p = 2 for second-order scheme), confirming consistent spatial discretisation behaviour. Results archived in supplementary verification report VR-2024-03."
