      "rationale": "Three hexahedral-dominant meshes generated (coarse: 4.1 M cells, medium: 9.8 M cells, fine: 22.4 M cells) with refinement ratio r = 1.5. GCI for NIH at the 4 L/min @ 3500 RPM operating point: GCI_fine = 3.1%, GCI_medium = 7.4%. Asymptotic range ratio = 0.98, confirming monotonic convergence. Fine mesh adopted for all production runs. Gradation 2 requirement met."
