      "rationale": "Predicted NIH compared to Morrison et al. (2019) experimental measurements across all operating points. Agreement within ±18% with no systematic directional bias (mean signed error +1.3%). The comparison dataset is from a centrifugal pump platform with similar impeller geometry and blood analogue fluid, providing a reasonable basis for output comparison at MRL 2. The assessment team noted the dataset's strong internal consistency and reproducibility across three independent experimental runs."
    },
    {
